  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You touch a quiver or ammo pouch containing arrows, bolts, or similar ammunition. When a target is hit by a ranged weapon attack using a piece of ammunition drawn from this container, the target takes an extra [[/r 1d6]] (your choice per attack) acid, cold, fire, lightning, or thunder damage. The spell's magic ends on the piece of ammunition when it hits or misses.</p><p><strong>At Higher Levels</strong>. When you cast this spell using a spell slot of 4th, 5th or 6th level, you can maintain your concentration on the spell for up to 8 hours. When you use a spell slot of 7th level or higher, you can maintain your concentration on the spell for up to 24 hours.</p>",
